        "rich_text_rJaBdp": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Introduction",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Jewellery trends change over time, but some designs return again and again because they carry deeper meaning. One such style that has gained renewed attention is the trilogy ring, also known as the three-stone ring. Instead of focusing on a single diamond, this ring features three stones placed side by side, creating a design that feels both balanced and symbolic.</p><p>In the past, trilogy rings were often chosen for milestone gifts or anniversaries. Today, they are becoming popular again, especially among people who want jewellery that represents more than just beauty. Many buyers are now looking for pieces that tell a story, and trilogy rings naturally do that.</p><p>At<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" Lucira Jewelry\"> Lucira Jewelry</a>, designs like the Three-Stone 0.91ct Round Diamond Ring, Pear Diamond Three-Stone Ring, and Hexa Baguette Trilogy Ring show how this classic style can feel both meaningful and modern.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qw7HLy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Trilogy Rings Symbolize Life’s Journey in a Simple Yet Powerful Way",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Trilogy Rings Symbolize Life’s Journey in a Simple Yet Powerful Way</h2><p>One of the biggest reasons trilogy rings are gaining attention again is their symbolism.</p><p>Traditionally, the three stones represent the past, the present, and the future. This interpretation resonates with many people because it reflects the story of a relationship or personal journey.</p>",
            "custom_id": "trilogy",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_A8fUE6": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Rich Text ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>1.] The first stone represents memories and experiences from the past.<br/><br/>2.] The center stone represents the present moment and the bond shared today.<br/><br/>3.] The third stone symbolizes the future and everything still to come.<br/><br/>Because of this meaning, trilogy rings are often chosen for engagements, anniversaries, or major life milestones.</p><p>Rings like the<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/products/three-stone-oval-anniversary-ring\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" Three-Stone Oval Anniversary Ring\"> Three-Stone Oval Anniversary Ring</a> beautifully capture this idea, making them a thoughtful gift for couples celebrating years together. </p>",
            "custom_id": "color",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
