        "rich_text_AJHQPB": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Many Buyers Want Jewellery That Feels Personal Rather Than Trendy",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Many Buyers Want Jewellery That Feels Personal Rather Than Trendy</h2><p>Another reason trilogy rings are becoming popular again is the shift in how people shop for jewellery.</p><p>Many buyers today prefer designs that feel personal and meaningful rather than purely trend-driven. Trilogy rings naturally fit this mindset because they tell a story through their structure.</p><p>For example, a ring like the Trio Flourish Ring may appear simple at first glance, but its three stones carry a deeper significance. The design feels elegant without needing excessive decoration.</p><p>This kind of subtle symbolism appeals to people who want jewellery with emotional value.</p>",
            "custom_id": "many",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_ry4cQt": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
