        },
        "rich_text_bhGzpc": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Trilogy Rings Offer a Balanced and Elegant Design",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Trilogy Rings Offer a Balanced and Elegant Design</h2>",
            "custom_id": "trilogy-rings",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qwTzXx": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Beyond symbolism, trilogy rings also have a visually pleasing structure.</p><p>The three stones create natural symmetry, which gives the ring a balanced appearance. Typically, the center diamond is slightly larger, while the two side stones frame it gently.</p><p>This arrangement helps the center stone stand out while still adding extra brilliance.</p><p>For instance, the Modern Trio Pear Diamond Ring uses three carefully placed stones to create a design that feels graceful and modern at the same time.</p><p>Because of this balanced layout, trilogy rings can feel both classic and contemporary.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_BiE3eV": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
