        "rich_text_mEE3FU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "They Provide Extra Sparkle Without Looking Overly Flashy",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>They Provide Extra Sparkle Without Looking Overly Flashy</h2><p>Some people want more brilliance than a simple solitaire ring offers, but they may not want a ring that feels too elaborate.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/trilogy-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Trilogy rings\">Trilogy rings</a> provide a good middle ground.</p><p>With three diamonds instead of one, the ring naturally reflects more light. At the same time, the design remains clean and structured.</p><p>A ring like the Multi-Shape Diamond Trilogy Ring shows how three stones can add sparkle without making the design feel heavy or crowded.</p><p>For many buyers, this balance between simplicity and brilliance is appealing.</p>",
            "custom_id": "they",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_XgNzg9": {
