        "rich_text_9LDfB8": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Modern Trilogy Rings Allow Creative Diamond Combinations",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Modern Trilogy Rings Allow Creative Diamond Combinations</h2><p>Another reason trilogy rings are attracting attention again is the flexibility in design.</p><p>Today’s rings don’t always use three identical diamonds. Designers often mix shapes to create more distinctive looks.</p>",
            "custom_id": "modern-trilogy",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_aMWUpF": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>For example:</p><p>1.] The Hexa Trillion Trilogy Ring uses triangular stones for a modern feel.<br/>2. The Pear Diamond Three-Stone Ring creates a softer, elegant silhouette.<br/>3.] The Emerald, Oval, and Round Diamond Trilogy Ring combines multiple shapes for a unique design.<br/><br/>These variations allow trilogy rings to feel fresh and contemporary while still keeping their symbolic meaning.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_78CQm3": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Trilogy Rings Are Perfect for Celebrating Milestones",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Trilogy Rings Are Perfect for Celebrating Milestones</h2><p>While many people choose trilogy rings as engagement rings, they are also popular for other occasions.</p><p>Some people receive them to mark important moments such as:</p>",
            "custom_id": "perfect",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_mLPJjQ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>1.] Anniversaries<br/>2.] Birthdays<br/>3.] Career milestones<br/>4.] Personal achievements<br/><br/>Because the three stones symbolize different stages of life, the ring becomes a reminder of meaningful experiences.</p><p>Designs like the Oval and <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/round-diamond\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Round Diamond \">Round Diamond </a>Trilogy Ring or the Green Gemstone and Round Diamond Trilogy Ring reflect this sense of celebration.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_jbgD4w": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Lucira’s Approach to Trilogy Ring Design",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Lucira’s Approach to Trilogy Ring Design</h2><p>At <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lucira Jewelry\">Lucira Jewelry</a>, trilogy rings are designed to combine symbolism with contemporary craftsmanship.</p><p>Each piece highlights the beauty of three diamonds while maintaining a refined and wearable design. Lucira rings feature IGI-certified lab-grown diamonds, ensuring exceptional brilliance along with responsible sourcing.</p><p>From classic three-stone rings to modern mixed-shape designs, Lucira trilogy rings are created to celebrate moments that matter.</p>",
            "custom_id": "luciras",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
